			<title>38th Annual Dinner Dance</title>
			<link>http://www.pontiangreeks.org/index.php/77-mega-content-demo/133-22nd-convention-of-the-pan-pontian-federation-of-usa-canada</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.pontiangreeks.org/index.php/77-mega-content-demo/133-22nd-convention-of-the-pan-pontian-federation-of-usa-canada</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;"><strong><img alt="" src="http://www.pontiangreeks.org/images/Screenshot_2015-09-19-19-48-17_1_1-1.jpg" height="579" width="453" /></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;"><strong>Save the Date</strong></span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">The Pontian Greek Society of Chicago's</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">38th Annual Dinner Dance</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;">Saturday October 10,2015</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Meridian Banquets 1701 W Algonquin Rd, Rolling Meadows, IL</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">6pm cocktails</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">7pm dinner</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">$80 adults</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">$35 children (12&amp; under)</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Our organization is honored to be hosting the 22nd Convention of the Pan Pontian Federation of USA &amp; Canada during the weekend of October 9-11, 2015.<br /></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Live Pontian Music – musicians from Greece, Boston &amp; New York!</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">For more information and to reserve your tables, please contact us at pontiangreeks@gmail.com or by phone at 312-945-9300 or 630-303-4361<br /></span></p></div>]]></description>
